com.versionone.om

Class Role

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.versionone.om.Entity
      • com.versionone.om.Role

  • public class Role
extends Entity
    List of roles allowed on a member.

    The id's of these roles must match the Role id's in the VersionOne system.
